      "# Discounted Cash Flow Estimation",
      "",
      "Discounted cash flow, 中文现金流折现, converts future cash generation into present value.",
      "",
      "## Discount Rate",
      "",
      "资本成本估计 combines debt and equity risk with an explicit capital structure assumption.",
      "",
      "## Aliases",
      "",
      "DCF, intrinsic value model, and 折现现金流法 refer to the same valuation family here.",
      "",
      "## Limits",
      "",
      "Terminal value should be stress-tested instead of treated as a precise forecast."
    ],
